dct_description_sm: United States. Army Map Service. United States. Army. Corps of Engineers. Alternate title: Nemours. In upper left margin: Nemours 1:10,000. Lambert conical orthomorphic projection. N.W. Africa zone grid. Relief shown by form lines at 20 meter intervals, and spot elevations. Compiled from the French H.O. chart No. 5873, 1932, 1:10,000. Topography from G.S.G.S. Sheet no. 238, 1942, 1:50,000. Revised from RAF aerial photos of Nemours and vicinity.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1942.
